Winter — a group exhibition: This group exhibition by Everard Read Cape Town brings patrons paintings and sculptures by artists including Skubalisto, Velaphi Mzimba, Sanell Aggenbach, Philip Barlow, Deborah Bell, Nic Blade and Ricky Dyaloyi. Details: The exhibition takes place until July 11 at Everard Read/Circa, 3 Portswood Road, V&A Waterfront, Cape Town.
